vh - Video History

USAGE:
    vh [-categories=cat1,cat2] [-date=YYYY/MM/DD] [-relative=days]

DESCRIPTION:
    Display video history from different categories. Shows metadata
    for videos in various states (downloaded, queued, watched, error).

OPTIONS:
    -categories=cat1,cat2
        Only include history from specified categories
        (default: downloaded, exit_with_error, queued, watched)

    -date=YYYY/MM/DD
        Only include history for specified date

    -relative=days
        Include history from relative number of days ago

EXAMPLES:
    vh
    vh -categories=downloaded,watched
    vh -date=2025/03/25
    vh -relative=7